      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，branch_1作为主分支放在中间，branch_0在最左边，branch_2和branch_3在右边。我需要开启分支显示和提交标签显示，方便看清每个commit。请问初始commit用什么标识？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "commit id"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "主分支先有一个commit标记为'x'，然后切到branch_2做两个commit 'a'和'b'，接着回branch_1做一个'y'，再去branch_3做'e'和'f'。branch_2之后要合并branch_1的内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit x",
        "commit a",
        "commit b",
        "commit y",
        "commit e",
        "commit f",
        "merge branch_1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，branch_2已经合并了branch_1。现在branch_0的情况呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_0",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "branch_0先做commit 'o'，然后branch_3要合并branch_2——因为branch_2已经包含了branch_1的最新内容。最后branch_0再做commit 'p'结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit o",
        "commit p",
        "merge branch_2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下流程：branch_3合并branch_2后，branch_0独立做最后的'p'提交。这样branch_0始终保持独立开发，没有参与任何合并对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_0",
        "commit p",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，branch_0是独立维护的分支。另外请把logLevel设成debug级别，方便后续检查渲染问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "logLevel",
